    "description": "<p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3082440/extras/ef882bc7b5187637c1577d37a536b094.poster.avif?t=1762970019\" width=600 height=250 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3082440/extras/ef882bc7b5187637c1577d37a536b094.webm?t=1762970019\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3082440/extras/ef882bc7b5187637c1577d37a536b094.mp4?t=1762970019\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3082440/extras/97998970e459e10d14f064d1a7f0120f.poster.avif?t=1762970019\" width=600 height=50 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3082440/extras/97998970e459e10d14f064d1a7f0120f.webm?t=1762970019\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3082440/extras/97998970e459e10d14f064d1a7f0120f.mp4?t=1762970019\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >迪恩·迪诺，黑帮头号前杀手，为了追求真正的梦想——开一家定制T恤店，选择逃离过去。这是他的新起点，新生活。但要彻底摆脱黑帮的阴影，并不容易。老大阿尔·萨朋突然出现，逼他偿还一笔巨额债务，只有还清债务，才能换取自由。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >迪恩·迪诺会不会为了守护这份新生活，重返黑帮的黑暗世界？而为什么经营这家不起眼的T恤店，对他意义重大？</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3082440/extras/b6e03142e23bd7d9ae9501b99d18be0a.poster.avif?t=1762970019\" width=600 height=50 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3082440/extras/b6e03142e23bd7d9ae9501b99d18be0a.webm?t=1762970019\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3082440/extras/b6e03142e23bd7d9ae9501b99d18be0a.mp4?t=1762970019\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >享受轻松有趣的小游戏，发挥创意，用丰富的贴纸打造专属你的布艺杰作。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3082440/extras/4e6bb88d374b21916c5acbd8d997dea2.poster.avif?t=1762970019\" width=600 height=250 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3082440/extras/4e6bb88d374b21916c5acbd8d997dea2.webm?t=1762970019\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3082440/extras/4e6bb88d374b21916c5acbd8d997dea2.mp4?t=1762970019\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3082440/extras/d36b155671a277a8667cbf9332840fa2.poster.avif?t=1762970019\" width=600 height=50 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3082440/extras/d36b155671a277a8667cbf9332840fa2.webm?t=1762970019\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3082440/extras/d36b155671a277a8667cbf9332840fa2.mp4?t=1762970019\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >了解顾客的喜好，或许还能发现他们不为人知的一面。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3082440/extras/b616a17a855750b7c85ba73ffe1a8f59.poster.avif?t=1762970019\" width=600 height=250 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3082440/extras/b616a17a855750b7c85ba73ffe1a8f59.webm?t=1762970019\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3082440/extras/b616a17a855750b7c85ba73ffe1a8f59.mp4?t=1762970019\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3082440/extras/5b31d64cb5f42b32c799caab8bcaa539.poster.avif?t=1762970019\" width=600 height=50 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3082440/extras/5b31d64cb5f42b32c799caab8bcaa539.webm?t=1762970019\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3082440/extras/5b31d64cb5f42b32c799caab8bcaa539.mp4?t=1762970019\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >在各种场景中，与迪恩·迪诺过去的黑帮势力正面交锋！</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3082440/extras/89222597b5aac1dd07a6104f93267a19.poster.avif?t=1762970019\" width=600 height=250 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3082440/extras/89222597b5aac1dd07a6104f93267a19.webm?t=1762970019\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3082440/extras/89222597b5aac1dd07a6104f93267a19.mp4?t=1762970019\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3082440/extras/e8b73b4c2e053427994ba2cf75f87414.poster.avif?t=1762970019\" width=600 height=50 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3082440/extras/e8b73b4c2e053427994ba2cf75f87414.webm?t=1762970019\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3082440/extras/e8b73b4c2e053427994ba2cf75f87414.mp4?t=1762970019\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >你可以选择经营一家正派的店铺，或者暗地里做点“灰色生意”。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3082440/extras/51cbb4320a11f85a01ab1f255d583f32.poster.avif?t=1762970019\" width=600 height=50 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3082440/extras/51cbb4320a11f85a01ab1f255d583f32.webm?t=1762970019\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3082440/extras/51cbb4320a11f85a01ab1f255d583f32.mp4?t=1762970019\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >根据你的选择和声誉，体验多结局的精彩故事。</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >设计独一无二的T恤，为顾客带来惊喜，收集各种特别的贴纸。</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >解锁更多贴纸，升级你的制作机器，提升效率。</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >每天努力生存，面对黑帮的威胁，偿还沉重债务，争取属于自己的自由。</p></li></ul>",
